elements.name: Como usuario quiero eliminar un tag

steps.name: I enter "ghost-author@example.com" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "Pruebas10automatizadas" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-btn-primary"
I enter "Kraken Tag For Delete" into input field having id "tag-name"
I enter "Kraken Tag for Delete Description" into input field having id "tag-description"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-btn-primary"
I should see text "Kraken Tag For Delete"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-btn-red"
I should see text "Are you sure you want to delete this tag"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-btn.gh-btn-red.gh-btn-icon.ember-view"
